WEBVTT

00:03:59.315 --> 00:04:02.205
not just in one or two villages
but the entire neighborhood.

00:04:02.205 --> 00:04:04.016
Millions of people camped there

00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:07.802
and sang devotional songs while the priest
flew about like a glider in the air.

00:04:09.240 --> 00:04:15.816
When he landed,
the entire crowd fell at his feet.

00:04:15.840 --> 00:04:18.721
People hailed and sang his praises,
loaded him with garlands

00:04:18.745 --> 00:04:22.362
to such an extent that the priest could
not get a glimpse of his own face.

00:04:22.386 --> 00:04:26.896
Gifts started pouring in,
40 bullock carts were loaded with them.

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:30.896
Now with these 40 bullock carts and garlands,